    <term><xref linkend="cha.boot"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Significantly shortened the chapter, because System V init has been
        replaced by systemd. systemd is now described in a separate chapter:
        <xref linkend="cha.systemd"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 10. The systemd daemon -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.systemd"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added a new chapter on systemd and the &yast; &ycc_runlevel;
        (Fate #316631, Fate #312568).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        New section on loading kernel modules
        (<link xlink:href="http://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=892349"/>).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
<!-- 11. journalctl: Query the systemd Journal -->
   <varlistentry>
    <term><xref linkend="cha.journalctl"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Added a new chapter
      (<link xlink:href="http://bugzilla.suse.com/show_bug.cgi?id=878352"/>).
     </para>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!--12. The Boot Loader GRUB 2 -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.grub2"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Replaced the GRUB Legacy documentation with a new chapter on &grub;.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Support for LILO has been dropped.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Added new section <xref linkend="sec.grub2.zseries"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 13. UEFI (Unified Extensible Firmware Interface) -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.uefi"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated the chapter and added new features (Fate #314510,
        Fate #316365).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
	Added instructions on where to find the &suse; Key certificate
        (Doc Comment #25080).
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>
   <varlistentry>
<!-- 15. Printer Operation -->
    <term><xref linkend="cha.p"/>
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Updated chapter and section according to new CUPS version and with PDF
